reviews.title: Takes a long time to load
reviews.comment: This app works perfectly for Siyah based kernel. I like the way it confirms any changes you have made to prevent any accidental modifications. It is understandable that the app takes a long time to load considering the amount of info it needs to collect. When you made any changes it prompts a small message box to confirm it. When you accidentally try to dismiss it by pressing the \"Go Back\" key, the app would exit and you would have to restart and the long long wait all over again. I think it is advisable to prompt a \"Confirm Exit\" box for programs that take such a long time to load.
